Package: VividVolcano
Type: Shiny Application
Title: Vivid Volcano: A Shiny App for Custom Analysis of Preprocessed Omics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tomasz", family = "StÄ™pkowski", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dzdzstepel@gmail.com")
Description: This Shiny application provides a customizable platform for the analysis of preprocessed omics data. 
  Targeted at non bioinformatitians it is aimed to provide a very smooth and intuitive UX enabling "wet lab"scientists to 
  handle crucial bioinformatic analyses on their own. It integrates data visualization, 
  statistical analyses,interactive tools and publication ready graphical outputs of plots and tables neatly formatted 
  to adhere to scientific standards.
